dc_title_s: Map to accompany application of Wildwood Land Company for a Riparian grant at Holly Beach, N.J.
dc_description_s: Map of North Wildwood showing the streets in the area, Beach Creek and Post Creek. Map also shows the sedge line, high water line, areas bare at low water, the low water line, and the exterior wharf lines. Map shows the proposed harbor and proposed inland waterway from Cape May to Bayhead
